### Full workflow: upload -> analyze -> download
# Select the `local` environment in the REST Client extension and update
# the variables in `rest-client.env.json` before running these requests.

### 1) Upload resume
# @name uploadResume
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ATSRefinerUploadBoundary

------ATSRefinerUploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="{{resumeFileName}}"
Content-Type: {{resumeContentType}}

< {{resumeFile}}
------ATSRefinerUploadBoundary--

### 2) Analyze uploaded resume
# @name analyzeResume
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{uploadResume.response.body.$.data.sessionId}}",
  "jobDescription": "{{jobDescription}}"
}

### 3) Download improved resume text
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/download/{{uploadResume.response.body.$.data.sessionId}}
